
Erica Rozetti is a second year political science major and the Recruitment Coordinator for ASUCD Lobby Corps. She is also in the sorority Delta Gamma.

She ran for ASUCD Senate in the Winter 2007 ASUCD Election with Timothy Silva. They did not want to win. Erica and Timothy Silva were not on the official LEAD slate, but they are LEAD supporters and wanted students to vote the official LEAD slate #1#6 then give them your #7 and #8 votes. Erica and Tim also endorsed Kareem Salem and Julie Hooper for ASUCD President and Vice President on their http://ucdavis.facebook.com/group.php?gid2235780354&refnf Facebook Group.
